data.description: RARE FIND * TURN-KEY INVESTMENT * Introducing a fully leased, newly constructed fourplex in the heart of Myrtle Beach. Each expansive 1200 square foot unit is thoughtfully designed, featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a spacious living area, a full-size kitchen, in-unit laundry, and an inviting porch. Upper units are enhanced by high vaulted ceilings. Perfectly situated in close proximity to local attractions and the beach, this property promises a profitable investment.
